article_title: Kickoff time set for ECU-Tulane football game
article_text:
The kickoff time has been set for the ECU-Tulane football game on Saturday, November 22nd.

The Pirates and Green Wave will kickoff at 3:30 inside Dowdy-Ficklen Stadium in Greenville.

The game will be broadcast online on ESPN3.
